downloadTitle: .NET Micro Framework Concepts, Prototypes, and Products
downloadDescription: Reviews the concepts, prototypes, and products shown at Embedded World 2008
detailsSection:
Support for this product is no longer available from Microsoft, please refer to http://www.netmf.com/forum/ for assistance.

Couldn't make it to Nuremburg for Embedded World 2008? We're bringing our booth to you with this description of concepts, prototypes, and products developed by Microsoft and its partners. Bonus: The latest development kits.
